<p class="ql-align-justify">活在世上弹指间，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">睁眼闭眼睁闭眼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">是是非非非非是，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大千世界万事现。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">难活三万六千天，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">何争争争伤心肝。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">名名利利是外物，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">人生得意须尽欢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">无功受禄可怜见，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">勤耕劳动幸福连。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">身健乐观在奉献，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">奉献光荣一百年。</p>